title: Guess I'll Never Know
lyrics:
Guess I’ll Never Know Lyrics 
[Verse 1] I never really know what's going on

There are the things I want you to know

Here we go 
You could take me there tonight

Whoa, I can't stay

And even when you're next to me 
I feel like you are gone 
[Chorus] It's all the things you never show 
There are the things I want you to know 
Secrets start in your heart so slow 
But if you don't want to tell me now 
I guess I'll never know 
[Outro] But if you don't want to tell me now 
I guess I'll never know
